ace because the breastplates and legs from these areas are some of the best armor pieces one can get, hence they are reserved for those of higher lvl.  Loot is only to be randomed on by alliance members.  However if every alliance member has gotten a piece already, then the loot passes down to invites, with the exception of exceptional items such as nice weapons, breastplates, and legs.  There are certain invites as well who attend almost every one of our raids that will get to random for loot on the discretion of the raid leaders.  Epic loot goes to whoever is farthest along or whoever has more seniority in a tie.  A new loot sytem based on points is currently being worked on and hopefully we will have it out soon.  Until then, this is the system in place.  Cheers!<br><br>-Dinekus Aleswigger<br>59 Myrmidon<br>Dragonslayers <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/udinekus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dinekus</A> at: 2/1/02 2:32:37 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fallianceraidforumfrm8.showPrevMessage?topicID=1.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <br><br><a self href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fallianceraidforumfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://home.swbell.net/kryson/allireply1.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fallianceraidforumfrm8.threadControl?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fallianceraidforumfrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fallianceraidforumfrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic>Unsub